Package: mcp
Title: Regression with Multiple Change Points
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Date: 2020-01-02
URL: http://lindeloev.github.io/mcp/
BugReports: https://github.com/lindeloev/mcp/issues
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jonas Kristoffer",
